# OPEN SOULS Learning App Environment Variables

# Required: Your OpenAI API key for LLM calls
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-api-key-here

# Optional: Use Anthropic instead
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-key

# Optional: Model preferences
# DEFAULT_MODEL=gpt-4
# QUALITY_MODEL=gpt-4
# FAST_MODEL=gpt-3.5-turbo

# Note: The local runner (npm run local) uses these keys directly
# without any cloud authentication or browser login! 